---
title: Sheet-Pan Hoisin Chicken and Veggies with Green Onion Rice
description: We’re big fans of sheet-pan baking for a healthier alternative to dinnertime cooking. But don’t worry, this dish is still jam-packed with flavour thanks to a sweet hoisin glaze, roasted green beans, and fluffy jasmine rice. One bite and you’ll be hooked.
